Happy #ValentinesDay! 💘 These deer from Kejimkujik National Park in Nova Scotia make for one of the cutest couples we know! 
Canada’s national parks and national historic sites offer some of the most romantic scenery, getaways and special activities; the perfect place to make lasting memories with that special someone.
